articles.title: European round-up: Barcelona beat Real Madrid to lift Spanish Super Cup | Atletico Madrid held by Almeria - Sky Sports
articles.description: Barcelona were crowned Spanish Super Cup champions after goals from Gavi, Robert Lewandowski and Pedri earned them a 3-1 win over rivals Real Madrid in Saudi Arabia.
articles.content:
